remarks:        --------------------------------------------------------
remarks:        RTIX on riigi hallatav dubleeriv interneti sõlmpunkt,
remarks:        mis ühendab omavahel Eesti internetivõrgud.
remarks:        Huvi korral võta ühendust help@ria.ee.

remarks:        RTIX is National State Network peering point located in Tallinn.
remarks:        RTIX connects public Estonian Internet networks.
remarks:        Its purpose is to ensure traffic between networks
remarks:        even if the connection with foreign countries is disrupted for any reason.
